{"tid":626465,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港澳辦否認一黨專政　被斥自欺欺人","createTime":"2018-04-12T06:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T07:36:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"12d09b9f67f1159bfc25e0b29c292c4a322fba25","tid":626465,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T06:39:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180412/20359189?_ga=2.75015058.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180412%2F20359189%3F_ga%3D2.75015058.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=yL4xyZaPfDSoAKiGF19RwRxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=f3c04ced\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180412%2F20359189%3F_ga%3D2.75015058.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=3b213aa5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180412/20359189?_ga=2.75015058.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港澳辦否認一黨專政　被斥自欺欺人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180412/large/12ls2p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180412%2Flarge%2F12ls2p3.jpg&h=91d2c677&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】人大常委譚耀宗早前稱叫結束一黨專政屬違憲，可能不可參選，日前訪京的律師會引述港澳辦副主任黃柳權（圖）稱，中國沒有一黨專政，認為反對一黨專政違憲是有誤解。支聯會主席何俊仁指，黃稱中國沒有一黨專政說法等同「皇帝的新衣」，只屬自欺欺人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何俊仁斥左派生事博利益<br />\n<br />\n律師會會長蘇紹聰日前分別與港澳辦副主任黃柳權及基本法委員會主任沈春耀會面，他會見記者時稱，他們曾與黃柳權討論內地修憲問題，對方指中國政治體系屬共產黨領導下的多黨合作模式，所以不存在一黨專政問題，又稱若指反對一黨專政的人違憲，當中存有誤解，但蘇紹聰稱雙方沒有談及，若有人提出結束一黨專政是否不能參選問題。<br />\n<br />\n雙方談到港大學者戴耀廷在台灣提出反專制運動成功後，香港及其他內地城市可以考慮獨立的言論，蘇引述黃稱，言論自由在香港得到保障，但也有限制。<br />\n<br />\n何俊仁反駁黃說法，指黃稱中國沒有一黨專政等同「皇帝的新衣」，「表面上話係多黨合作制，實際係一黨專政，咁樣講屬自欺欺人」，何亦指今次黃說法反映香港一班左派聲稱叫結束一黨專政的人不能參選，並非中央意見，批評左派、土共企圖製造事端，想挑動社會矛盾，他們就可從中博取政治利益。<br />\n<br />\n■記者莫劍弦  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n倘五泛民議員缺席　議案勢通過<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n傳韓正掌港澳工作協調小組"},{"pid":"ec748847a1c1f71342f93ff77648c1b7836baa2c","tid":626465,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T07:36:28.000Z","msg":"硬膠泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3124d977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff15f2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=27225035&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}